4
00:04:59,555 --> 00:05:01,671
Do you want me to catch pneumonia?

5
00:05:12,715 --> 00:05:15,513
Don't just stand there, Freddy.
Go and find a cab.

6
00:05:15,795 --> 00:05:17,751
All right, l'll get one.

7
