She wants her things sent over...

713
00:46:57,035 --> 00:46:59,105
...to 27A Wimpole Street...

714
00:47:00,155 --> 00:47:02,146
...care of Professor Higgins.

715
00:47:02,235 --> 00:47:03,429
[Mrs. Hopkins laughs]

716
00:47:03,515 --> 00:47:05,426
An' what things does she want?

717
00:47:05,955 --> 00:47:08,344
Her birdcage and her Chinese fan.

718
00:47:10,955 --> 00:47:12,024
[Laughing]

719
00:47:12,115 --> 00:47:13,753
MRS. HOPKlNS: But she says:

720
00:47:13,835 --> 00:47:16,508
"Never mind about sending any clothes."

721
00:47:18,235 --> 00:47:19,588
[Laughing]

722
00:47:20,475 --> 00:47:23,114
l knew she had a career in front of 'er.

723
00:47:23,355 --> 00:47:25,311
We're in for a booze-up.

724
00:47:25,795 --> 00:47:27,831
The sun is shining on Alfred P. Doolittle.

725
00:47:27,915 --> 00:47:29,394
